<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 37. Labels. i Bulimus martinicensis Pfeiffer, 1846 ii Bulimus meleagris Pfeiffer, 1853 iii Bulimus mejillonensis Pfeiffer in Pfeiffer and Dunker, 1857 iv Bulimus meridanus Pfeiffer, 1846 v Bostryx metagyra Pilsbry & Olsson, 1949 vi Bulimus mollicellus Reeve, 1849 vii Bulimus monachus Pfeiffer, 1857 viii Bulimulus (Bostryx) moniezi Dautzenberg, 1896 ix Bulimus montagnei d'Orbigny, 1837." , "Figure 1. Bostryx species. A Bostryx umbilicaris (Souleyet, 1842), paralectotype NHMUK 1854.7.24.359 (H = 13.3) B Bostryx moniezi (Dautzenberg, 1896), syntype NHMUK 1908.6.13.22 (H = 12.46) C-D Bostryx infundibulum (Pfeiffer, 1853), lectotype NHMUK 1975163 (H = 18.25) E Bostryx scalaricosta (Morelet, 1860), lectotype NHMUK 1893.2.4.1170 (H = 15.5) F Bostryx hamiltoni (Reeve, 1849), lectotype NHMUK 1849.5.14.53 (H = 17.0) G-H Bostryx lesueurianus (Morelet, 1860), syntype NHMUK 1893.2.4.1182 (H = 22.5) I Bostryx pygmaeus costatus Weyrauch, 1960, paratype NHMUK 1975357 (H = 8.45) J Bostryx imeldae costifer Weyrauch, 1960, paratype NHMUK 1975354 (H = 9.6) K Bostryx metagyra Pilsbry & Olsson, 1949, paratype NHMUK 20100630 (H = 7.1). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26804" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26608" .

